    • Field Detail

      • rawData

        private static final java.lang.String[][][] rawData
        Source of the tromino data. - The first index is the thetromino type. - The second index is the rotation. Some tetromino's data is the same in different rotations. These duplicated mask are not included, because rotating is cyclic, so it is easy to work without them. - The third index and the character position specify a 2D matrix which stores the mask. X means there is a part of that tetromino data, space means there isn't.
